summary: This document is a certificate of true copy from the Department of Transportation regarding records of the Raytheon Aircraft Company 400A. It certifies the authenticity of the records related to the aircraft's registration and is signed by a legal custodian.

persons.name: Michelle Endsley
persons.context: Michelle Endsley is identified as the Supervisory Legal Instruments Examiner who certified the authenticity of the aircraft records.

persons.name: Evin St
persons.context: Evin St is mentioned as the Acting Manager who has affixed their name and seal to the certificate.

keyFacts: The document certifies the authenticity of records pertaining to the Raytheon Aircraft Company 400A.
The certificate was signed on August 23, 2021.
Michelle Endsley is the legal custodian of the records.
The document is subject to protective orders as indicated.
